        <title>ACTIVITY: “Noughts and Crosses” and Module Test</title>
        <para id="id1164016004170">26. Let us play “Noughts and Crosses”!</para>
        <para id="id1164010028242">You need a friend and a rectangle with decimal numbers as in the example. </para>
        <para id="id1164011304061">You may also write your own decimal numbers in the blocks.</para>
        <list id="id1164010028299" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Player 1 chooses any number on the rectangle and must say what number ÷ or × by 10, 100 or 1 000 will give that number.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1164011394786">e.g. 2,5 : 25 ÷ 10 = 2,5 or</para>
        <para id="id1164017559066">  0,025 ´ 100 = 2,5</para>
