        <list id="id1164009973280" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Player 2 checks with the calculator.</item>
          <item>If player 1 is correct, he marks his block with a x or o. </item>
          <item>Take turns until one of the players is the first one to get 4 x’s or o’s in a row. (horizontal, vertical or diagonal).</item>
